ttps://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/075443_9af1ab6864d03b8407c1ab1085fc2580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F075443_9af1ab6864d03b8407c1ab1085fc2580.jpg&h=95e9733d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n申請幾多股藍表"},{"pid":"423666342ea10832c491695e30a227950e5561cd","tid":461654,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:02:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>優先認購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/075443_9af1ab6864d03b8407c1ab1085fc2580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F075443_9af1ab6864d03b8407c1ab1085fc2580.jpg&h=95e9733d&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n申請幾多股藍表</blockquote><br />\n200 only <br />\n利申只持有200股700<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1e7a51f61128f7c542e66e12805d25f68fa222b","tid":461654,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006c555ad3cde0017b4431a461071d75ea3e4cb2","tid":461654,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:11:31.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"fa96fbb6d4c893bcfff7789e90b3f17ec929e322","tid":461654,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:12:01.000Z","msg":"騰訊股東優先認購分派超預期<br />\n文章日期：2017年11月8日   <br />\n【明報專訊】騰訊（0700）股東可用手上股份優先認購閱文，成為這場抽新股浪潮中的大贏家，配售結果顯示，有股東認購100萬股，最終獲分配21.5萬股，按昨日暗盤收市價計算，帳面已賺761萬元。<br />\n<br />\n有股東獲派21萬股 帳賺761萬<br />\n<br />\n閱文在優先發售認購的藍表部分，一共錄得4.49億股申請，超額約59.42倍，閱文最終分派合共756.86萬股予騰訊股東，佔總發行股份的5%，扣除按每持有1256股騰訊可認購1股閱文比例分派部分，超額認購的分貨比例明顯較公開發售部分優勝，撇除透過中央結算系統的申請，認購10手以下的獲分派率為100%，最大手認購100萬股獲得分派率為21.5%，與公開發售部分的單位數字中籤率明顯見分野。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊股東認購閱文設定的門檻，是每持有1256股股份可優先認購1股閱文股份，以每手200股計，需持市值近1億元騰訊股份才可肯定獲發一手；不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">只要股東持有1256股騰訊，已可申請超額認購閱文，意味其實只要持有市值約50萬元騰訊股份，已握有一張超額認購「入場券」。</span><br />\n<br />\n豐盛金融資產管理董事黃國英坦言後悔，他未有透露自己獲分派多少閱文股份，不過「對結果有少少失望」，但指當初應將資金全數透過優先認購入表。他指分派得宜的原因是因為指數追蹤資金持有大量騰訊，但不能認購閱文，故在此部分較多股份留予其他股東申請超額認購，造成明顯佔優的局面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1510083121840&amp;issue=20171108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Fdaily2.php%3Fnode%3D1510083121840%26issue%3D20171108&d=AOP3rO6paCFAFoPnom7SaP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=6a89a0ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/daily2.php?node=1510083121840&amp;issue=20171108</a>"},{"pid":"e9bde5a302d9fa249cfec1199ba7401ef0c9c7ec","tid":461654,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>......</blockquote><br />\n好過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1bc799060a244b613d5a1765c2aac763923edd","tid":461654,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:12:25.000Z","msg":"額外認購唔係100%中咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec976a10598f9a4c8a8d765164b85e3cd379e41","tid":461654,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:13:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>額外認購唔係100%中咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n更正，細額果啲"},{"pid":"74802f5fc93d4d81f2cd484982a8d657c15dd8ad","tid":461654,"uid":151378,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:13:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0f8036bd36b360f11417be1b68dd9fa3f482509","tid":461654,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T00:13:22.000Z","